original_title: Old Time Rock 'n' Roll: Legends In Concert
overview: Some of the biggest Rock and Roll stars are united on this mesmerizing compilation. Recorded at the Rock and Roll Palace, artists who performed include Brian Hyland with 'Ginny Come Lately,' 'The Dovells' with 'The Bristol Stomp, Del Shannon with 'Runaway' and many more.
tagline: Old Time Rock 'n' Roll: Legends In Concert
title: Old Time Rock 'n' Roll: Legends In Concert
